name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
    t1.DOMAINS,
    t1.PERSONNAME,
    t1.POSTID,
    t1.POSTNAME,
    t1.TEAMID,
    t1.TEAMMEMBERID,
    t1.TEAMNAME,
    t1.USERID,
    t1.USERNAME
FROM (SELECT
          t1.DC as DOMAINS,
          t21.DISPLAY_NAME as PERSONNAME,
          null as POSTID,
          null as POSTNAME,
          t1.ORGANIZATIONAL_ROLE_ID as TEAMID,
          t1.ID as TEAMMEMBERID,
          t11.NAME as TEAMNAME,
          t1.PERSON_ID as USERID,
          t21.UID as USERNAME
      FROM sys_member t1
               LEFT JOIN sys_organizational_role t11 ON t1.ORGANIZATIONAL_ROLE_ID = t11.ID
               LEFT JOIN sys_person t21 ON t1.PERSON_ID = t21.ID
     ) t1
